# JDH Gas — environment variables
# Copy to .env.local and fill in. The site works without these (graceful fallbacks);
# set them before launch to enable live email + live Google reviews.

# --- Enquiry form email (Resend) ---
# Without this, the contact form validates and logs to the server but does NOT email.
# Get a key at https://resend.com and verify the jdhgas.co.uk domain.
RESEND_API_KEY=

# --- Live Google reviews (Google Places API, New) ---
# Without this, the reviews section shows the 3 verified reviews + the 5.0/24 aggregate.
# With it, the section shows the live rating + total count + up to 5 reviews (Google's cap).
# Enable "Places API (New)" in Google Cloud + a billing account (free monthly credit applies).
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=
# Optional: skip the lookup by pinning the Place ID (find via Google's Place ID Finder).
GOOGLE_PLACE_ID=
